        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil half a kettle</p><p>Trim, then slice your<strong> spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Top, tail, peel and chop your <strong>carrot[s]</strong> into batons</p><p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
