    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pork meatballs are cooked through and browned, transfer to a plate and set aside</p><p>Return the pan to a medium heat and add the <strong>chopped pepper </strong>and <strong>carrot batons </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
