      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have softened, add your <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>to the pan and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong>, <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>pork meatballs </strong>and <strong>sweet & sour sauce</strong> and cook for 1 min further or until the pork meatballs are coated in sauce – these are your <strong>sweet & sour pork meatballs</strong></p>",
